d_Financial_Statement_tc.pdf" class="downloadLink">綜合財務報表附註</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '財務', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'financials-tc', '', '', '2013-07-16 10:19:48', '2013-07-16 10:19:48', '', 0, 'http://tti.sedgwick-richardson.net/?page_id=131', 0, 'page', '', 0),
